{/* PAYOUTS SECTION                                                     */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "payouts" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-4">
    The profit split is <strong>80/20 in the trader's favour</strong>. Withdrawals are processed <strong>once a week on Wednesdays</strong>, with the request due by 2pm on the prior Friday. Minimum net withdrawal is <strong>$100</strong>. Withdrawal methods are <strong>assigned by the firm</strong> and are not optional.
